name: Alien aliens
description:
It's a 1-2 minutes experience, explore the ship. Jump into portal for an end.

Made in bipsi game maker HD (bitsy clone) for a Low Effort Jam 22

Controls:

  •  PC: arrows or WASD to move and interact
  • Mobile: swipe up/down/left/right to move and interact

How to play:

  • bump into everything interesting
  • enjoy the experience

Credits:

Art/logic - me

Music - Dubstep Light by Jason Shaw from Audionautix.com
